title: F1 2011 Race 4 Turkey Qualifying HD 1080 H264 AC3
description:
Formula One 2011 Season

Turkey Grand Prix Qualifying in High Definition

Race 4: Turkish Grand Prix, Istanbul Park Curcuit

Record Source: BBC One HD
Original Format: MPEG TS Stream
Date: Saturday 07th May 2011
Time: 11:00 to 13:30

Jake Humphrey, Martin Brundle, David Coulthard & Eddie Jordan present the F1 Qualifying coverage to the 4th Race
meeting of the 2011 Formula One season, The Turkish Grand Prix, from the Instanbul Park Curcuit.

Please Note: The BBC Broadcast had audio problems at the beginning of the coverage for around 5 minutes or so the sound 
is very quiet and sometimes cuts out, which they do apologise for!

This is not an encoding error on my behalf.. Bear with it! 
Within a few mimutes the volume level is returned to normal for the remainder of the coverage.

For anyone who need it, or those unfamiliar with playing HD quality on their PC,
Ive included this first upload with an excellent player for MKV h.264 encoded media.
Included in the torrent is VLC Media Player v1.1.9, just install and play! You can additionally
install the AC3 filter for those using a home theatre system for digital passthrough AC3>SPDIF output

Video: The Video is encoded using AVC/H.264 into a mkv container
Audio: The audio is now Dolby Digital. Support for AC3 codec (2 channels as Live broadcasts are not 5.1)
